font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Khách Nước Ngoài</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width="310" style="width:232.5pt;padding:0in 0in 0in 0in">\r\n  <p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n  line-height:normal"><font size="2"><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">3.600.000VND</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">GIÁ TOUR BAO GỒM:</span></u></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Xe ô tô du lịch 7-16-29-35-45 chỗ đời mới điều\r\nhòa, lái xe chuyên nghiệp (kinh nghiệm nhiệt tình, văn minh, lịch sự).</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Khách sạn 3 sao, tiêu chuẩn 2 người 1 phòng,\r\ntrường hợp lẻ nam, nữ ngủ ghép phòng 3. Trường hợp đi 1 người bắt buộc phụ thu\r\nphòng đơn (VN*: phụ thu 750.000đ/ 3 đêm; NN*: phụ thu 900.000VND/ 3 đêm).</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Khách sạn 3 sao – Đà Nẵng</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">: Tiến Thịnh, Bay Sydney, Luna Diamond, Royal…</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Khách sạn 3 sao – Huế:</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;Duy Tân 1, 2, Ngọc Hương, New Star, Thanh\r\nUyên…</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Ăn 07 bữa chính: 4 bữa trưa, 3 bữa tối tiêu\r\nchuẩn 120.000Đ/người, 3 bữa sáng Buffet tại khách sạn.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Nước uống (02 chai lavie nhỏ/ngày) phục vụ trên\r\nxe theo trong suốt hành trình thăm quan.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Hướng dẫn viên chuyên nghiệp theo đoàn phục vụ\r\nsuốt tuyến.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Vé thăm quan thắng cảnh tại tất cả các điểm thăm\r\nquan theo chương trình.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Bảo hiểm mức đển bù tối đa 20.000.000Đ/người/vụ.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Thuế giá trị gia tăng 10% (VAT)</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">GIÁ TOUR KHÔNG BAO GỒM:</span></u></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Đồ uống (rượu, bia, nước ngọt...) trong các bữa\r\năn và suốt chương trình.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Chi phí Vé máy bay/ vé tàu khứ hồi: Hà Nội/ TP\r\nHồ Chí Minh – Đà Nẵng - Hà Nội/ TP Hồ Chí Minh.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Vé cáp treo khứ hồi Bà Nà (500.000VND/ 1 khách).</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Các chi phí cá nhân (điện thoại, giặt là, mua\r\nsắm, thăm quan ngoài chương trình...).</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Tiền thưởng (Tip) cho lái xe, hướng dẫn viên\r\n(không bắt buộc).</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">GIÁ TOUR TRẺ EM:</span></u></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Đối với giá tour chưa bao gồm vé máy bay:</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Dưới 05 tuổi: miễn phí hoàn toàn (bố mẹ tự chăm\r\nsóc, phát sinh bố mẹ tự thanh toán).</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">05 – 08 tuổi: giá tour bằng 50% giá tour người\r\nlớn.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">09 – 11 tuổi: giá tour bằng 75% giá tour người\r\nlớn.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">12 tuổi trở lên: bằng giá tour người lớn.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Quy định vé máy bay:</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Dưới 02 tuổi: 10% giá vé người lớn.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 43.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black;">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]